<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Housewarming Invitation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        .invitation {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 2rem;
            max-width: 400px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            margin: auto;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #4a4a4a;
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        h4 {
            color: #4a4a4a;
            font-size: 1.35rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        p {
            color: #666666;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .highlight {
            color: #3498db;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            h1 {
                font-size: 1.75rem;
            }
            h4 {
                font-size: 1.15rem;
            }
            p {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
        } @media (min-width: 481px) {
            .invitation {
                border: 1px solid #ddd;
                box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="invitation">
        <div class="icon">üè°</div>
        <h4>Sebastian & Joanna's</h4>
        <h1>Housewarming Party!</h1>
        <p>Join us as we celebrate our new home!</p>
        <p>
            <span class="highlight">When:</span> <%= date %> <%= time %>
        </p>
        <p>
            <span class="highlight">Where:</span> <%= location %>
        </p>
        <p>We can't wait to share our new space with you. Come enjoy good company, refreshments, and make yourself at home!</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
